Package: blesh
Version: 0.4.0-devel4
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Alienkrishn [Anon4You]
Depends: git, make, termux-tools
Section: shells
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/akinomyoga/ble.sh
Description: Bash Line Editor (ble.sh) – interactive command line editing
 ble.sh is a command-line editor for Bash that provides syntax highlighting,
 command completion, and improved editing capabilities. It replaces the
 default GNU Readline with a more feature-rich interface written in pure Bash.
